[CENTER][SIZE=6][B]🐱 CatsAndMice - Red light, green light with moderators[/B][/SIZE]
[SIZE=4]A competitive click game for your Minecraft server[/SIZE][/CENTER]

[CENTER][IMG]https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Loot1/CatsAndMice/master/.github/assets/image.png[/IMG][/CENTER]

[SIZE=5][B]📖 What is CatsAndMice?[/B][/SIZE]

CatsAndMice is a Minecraft adaptation of the original [URL='https://github.com/Seblor/Cats-n-Mice']Cats-n-Mice Discord bot[/URL] by [B]Seblor[/B].

Players click a hologram to increase a shared score. Moderators (cats 🐱) can reset the score at any time — the goal for players (mice 🐭) is to reach the highest score possible before it gets wiped! The current score and last clicks are displayed in real-time on a clickable hologram.

[SIZE=5][B]✨ Features[/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*][B]Clickable hologram[/B] — real-time leaderboard powered by DecentHolograms
[*][B]Role-based gameplay[/B] — mice click to increase the score, cats reset it
[*][B]Click cooldown[/B] — configurable delay between each click (default: 5 minutes)
[*][B]Best score tracking[/B] — records the best score with the player name, date and time
[*][B]Mock (fake) player names[/B] — automatically fills empty hologram slots to keep the display full
[*][B]Configurable display order[/B] — most recent click at the bottom or at the top
[*][B]LuckPerms support[/B] — displays rank prefixes next to player names in the hologram
[*][B]Discord webhook alerts[/B] — sends a notification when a score threshold is reached
[*][B]Fully customizable[/B] — every message, color and setting is configurable in [ICODE]config.yml[/ICODE]
[*][B]Async data saving[/B] — click history and hologram location are saved automatically
[/LIST]

[SIZE=5][B]🚀 Installation[/B][/SIZE]
[LIST=1]
[*]Make sure [URL='https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/96927/']DecentHolograms[/URL] is installed on your server
[*]Download the [B]CatsAndMice[/B] JAR and place it in your [ICODE]plugins/[/ICODE] folder
[*]Start or restart your server
[*]Stand where you want the hologram and run [ICODE]/mice create[/ICODE]
[*]Edit [ICODE]plugins/CatsAndMice/config.yml[/ICODE] to customize messages and settings
[*]Run [ICODE]/mice reload[/ICODE] to apply your changes
[/LIST]

[SIZE=5][B]⚙️ Commands & Permissions[/B][/SIZE]

[B]Commands:[/B]
[LIST]
[*][ICODE]/mice create[/ICODE] — Creates the game hologram at your location ([ICODE]catsandmice.create[/ICODE])
[*][ICODE]/mice reload[/ICODE] — Reloads the configuration ([ICODE]catsandmice.reload[/ICODE])
[*][ICODE]/mice help[/ICODE] — Displays the help menu ([ICODE]catsandmice.help[/ICODE])
[/LIST]
[B]Permissions:[/B]
[LIST]
[*][ICODE]catsandmice.mice[/ICODE] — Allows clicking the hologram to increase the score
[*][ICODE]catsandmice.cat[/ICODE] — Allows clicking the hologram to reset the score
[*][ICODE]catsandmice.bypass[/ICODE] — Bypasses the click cooldown delay
[*][ICODE]catsandmice.*[/ICODE] — Grants all plugin permissions (OP by default)
[/LIST]

[SIZE=5][B]🔗 Discord Webhook (optional)[/B][/SIZE]

CatsAndMice can send an alert to a Discord channel when the score reaches a configurable threshold.
[LIST=1]
[*]Create a webhook in your Discord channel settings
[*]Set [ICODE]webhook.enabled: true[/ICODE] in [ICODE]config.yml[/ICODE]
[*]Paste your webhook URL in [ICODE]webhook.url[/ICODE]
[*]Set your score threshold with [ICODE]webhook.threshold[/ICODE]
[/LIST]

[SIZE=5][B]📦 Dependencies[/B][/SIZE]
[LIST]
[*][URL='https://www.spigotmc.org/resources/96927/'][B]DecentHolograms[/B][/URL] — [COLOR=Red]Required[/COLOR]
[*][URL='https://luckperms.net/'][B]LuckPerms[/B][/URL] — [COLOR=Gray]Optional[/COLOR] (for rank prefix display in hologram)
[/LIST]
[B]Server:[/B] Spigot / Paper 1.20.6 or higher — [B]Java 17+[/B]

